# themeIdentifier

**Instance Property**

The product theme identifier of the originating Apple Print Product.

## Declaration

```swift
var themeIdentifier: String? { get }
```

## Creating a Project from an Apple Print Product

- **brandingEnabled**: A Boolean value indicating whether branding was enabled in the source project.
- **pageNumbersEnabled**: A Boolean value indicating whether page numbering was enabled in the source project.
- **productIdentifier**: The product identifier of the originating Apple Print Product.
